#    - All NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are exposed to browser
#    - NEVER put secrets in NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables
#    - Keep sensitive keys on backend only (.env without NEXT_PUBLIC_)

# 6. BUILD & DEPLOYMENT
#    - Run: npm run build
#    - Check for errors - if build fails, check env variables
#    - Deploy via PM2 or Next.js hosting service

# 7. TESTING BEFORE GOING LIVE
#    - Test with restricted market hours (before 9:15 AM)
